"},"type":"backlink","position":{"start":{"line":8,"column":33,"offset":345},"end":{"line":8,"column":84,"offset":396},"indent":[]},"value":"mesh-resource.node-component.flow.node-metadata"}],"anchors":{"use-of-_node-handle-in-metapayload-flows":{"type":"header","text":"Use of _node-handle in metapayload flows","value":"use-of-_node-handle-in-metapayload-flows","line":14,"column":0,"depth":2},"recommended-vocabulary":{"type":"header","text":"Recommended vocabulary","value":"recommended-vocabulary","line":18,"column":0,"depth":2}},"children":[],"parent":"node-flow","data":{}},"body":"<h1 id=\"metapayload-flow\">metapayload flow<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#metapayload-flow\"></a></h1>\n<p>A <strong>metapayload flow</strong> contains system-related administrative and structural metadata for every <a href=\"/sflo/notes/mesh-node\">mesh node</a>, including the versioning data for each node's flows.</p>\n<p>In the filesystem, it exists as a <a href=\"/sflo/notes/node-metadata-flow-folder\">_node-metadata-flow folder</a> in a <a href=\"/sflo/notes/hp9ckpez0pmuv270sn005gt\">node folder</a>.</p>\n<p>Mesh-specific metadata about a node's flows' <a href=\"/sflo/notes/r6akf3zjimf3ubkxpqmeubc\">version snapshot</a>s mostly lives here too, eliminating the need to keep separate metadata in the node component. Also may contain metadata about the assets folder.</p>\n<h2 id=\"use-of-_node-handle-in-metapayload-flows\">Use of _node-handle in metapayload flows<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#use-of-_node-handle-in-metapayload-flows\"></a></h2>\n<p>When metapayload flows (or any <a href=\"/sflo/notes/system-facet\">system facet</a> dataset) refer to mesh nodes, they'll usually be talking about \"the-node-as-mesh-constituent\", so they'll use the node's <a href=\"/sflo/notes/wie8wazi0eoq81zke09czxk\">node handle</a> identifier</p>\n<h2 id=\"recommended-vocabulary\">Recommended vocabulary<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#recommended-vocabulary\"></a></h2>\n<hr>\n<strong>Backlinks</strong>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/sflo/notes/mesh-resource\">mesh resources</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/sflo/notes/h6ssv16gdyf56gg235dxv85\">semantic mesh</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/sflo/notes/concept-summary\">Concept Summary</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/sflo/notes/why-are-there-components-at-the-top-of-a-repo\">Why are there components at the top of a repo?</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/sflo/notes/osqi7xn4mw3j9v0kvsoc5uo\">Why Dont payload nodes Contain Distributions Directly</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/sflo/notes/j5we7en2hdwvax2ricv2u00\">Handling Renaming</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/sflo/notes/node-metadata-flow-folder\">_node-metadata-flow folder</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/sflo/notes/9c27yly4ed3ju7msf8luhge\">node component</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/sflo/notes/mesh-node\">mesh node</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/sflo/notes/p3mbdrze0qe8uvko4i16t1s\">folder resource facet</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/sflo/notes/6ki4upsdymjb9vy82oec2cf\">dataset facet</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/sflo/notes/node-flow\">node flow</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/sflo/notes/0n1lq6aq1gskj46bpcx9h4h\">snapshot distribution</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/sflo/notes/payload-node\">paylod node</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/sflo/notes/63tfb27btzbph10tpvckz7b\">sflo-api plugin</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/sflo/notes/payload-flow\">payload flow</a></li>\n</ul>","noteIndex":{"id":"voy7zrf0f6bs86m02uadhaf","title":"Semantic Flow Documentation","desc":"","updated":1756155165637,"created":1755709990079,"custom":{"nav_order":0,"permalink":"/"},"fname":"root","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":"documentation","selfContained":false,"name":"sflo"},"contentHash":"05284b47f8aa47c962f0ff2a3c3ac13a","links":[{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"root","id":"voy7zrf0f6bs86m02uadhaf","vaultName":"sflo"},"value":"now","position":{"start":{"line":4,"column":1,"offset":107},"end":{"line":4,"column":8,"offset":114},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"now"}},{"